{"tid":1249181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[西班牙法官下令發佈對江澤民李鵬逮捕令]","createTime":"2019-06-21T16:00:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T01:32:07.000Z","uid":95565,"like":99,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a9b5c40c19c66b3c96bc1e9a61633f62a1e19a57","tid":1249181,"uid":95565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:00:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/china/2014/02/140210_spain_china_jiang\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchina%2F2014%2F02%2F140210_spain_china_jiang&d=ow9JOMNIA3MeF92spim0Pgu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=99b71a62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchina%2F2014%2F02%2F140210_spain_china_jiang&h=0d7d80bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/china/2014/02/140210_spain_china_jiang</a><br />\n<br />\n2014年 2月 10日<br />\n<br />\n據路透社報道，西班牙最高法院的法官周一（10日）下令發佈對中國前國家主席江澤民、前總理李鵬和其他被指在西藏犯有反人類罪行官員的國際逮捕令。<br />\n<br />\n這一訴訟案是由人權組織提出的，因為西班牙的法律系統比較獨特，該國承認「普遍管轄原則」，也就是不管什麼人在世界任何地方犯下反人類罪，都可以被越國界起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有冇人幫我地去信西班牙聰聰(盧偉聰)係西班牙提升知名度呀?</span></span>"},{"pid":"3c10d2de9e7727ddd1060891a5dfa81d29686727","tid":1249181,"uid":95565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:01:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92319b6add1641ea3891d2fb9d86f2de250a34de","tid":1249181,"uid":95565,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b6697264b36b125e0d0a1432099c82de0f9c8e","tid":1249181,"uid":134438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568d7e9336a994ee8bbb2f77ec66114e6be292de","tid":1249181,"uid":95